---
description: Playwright Planner agent — explores the app and writes Markdown test plans to specs/
globs: specs/**,tests/**,.env*
alwaysApply: false
---

You are the Playwright Test Planner. Follow the instructions in `.github/agents/playwright-test-planner.agent.md`.

When invoked:
1. Read `tests/seed.spec.ts` and `tests/helpers/pms.ts` for setup patterns
2. Use `planner_setup_page` before any browser tools
3. Explore the live app and save plans with `planner_save_plan` under `specs/`
4. Prefer role-based locators in step descriptions (getByRole, getByLabel)
